description: Unique and spacious convertible studio with a separate space for a bedroom. Recently renovated kitchen and bath. Lovely views of Millennium Park and the city. World-class building with many amazing amenities, including pool, expansive outdoor patio with grills, gym, basketball court, playroom for kids, door staff, and more!
